{"tid":649481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你老味 51勞動節","createTime":"2018-05-01T15:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T15:44:45.000Z","uid":125333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"903081e116c510fc12ce9e034600cec4b33c4f83","tid":649481,"uid":125333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"報左今日返工仲以為係普通平日 炒埸炒個lunch 班ol就算 一落到鋪頭成堆家庭嘅客 仆街原來係51勞動節班ol放假 做撚到仆街 <br />\n又有一堆細路係度落單 落到燥 買2個包第一個走沙律醬同芥辣 第二個包淨係走芥辣都可以講到成Pat屎 卡撚住哂完全表達唔到 問佢家長又唔應 仲有問係堂食定拎走10個有5個唔撚應 都唔明細路表達能力咁差<br />\nOl你地真好落單又快 又識do互相尊重又唔吹單 快啲上辦公室快啲食快啲返去做嘢👍🏻<br />\n今日返10個小時 9.5小時都係炒緊埸 做撚到三萬五<br />\n你老味勞動節on9<br />\n利申：高級快餐店"},{"pid":"ee9607055f7b781da211da9f3db000d1bb080c87","tid":649481,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"你表達能力同細路差唔多"},{"pid":"5a561fae8ddebc5bba4b005a1e8e43bbb35281b0","tid":649481,"uid":125333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee9607055f7b781da211da9f3db000d1bb080c87","tid":649481,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"你表達能力同細路差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"發洩下姐 做到咁攰"},{"pid":"7bfcec16165044bda7b0e6034e6af044f0543b27","tid":649481,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a561fae8ddebc5bba4b005a1e8e43bbb35281b0","tid":649481,"uid":125333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee9607055f7b781da211da9f3db000d1bb080c87","tid":649481,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"你表達能力同細路差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"發洩下姐 做到咁攰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}